SELECT mean("sockets_used") as "used",mean("sockets_total") as "total" FROM "rabbitmq_node" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval),* fill(null)

list.name: Environnement
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES from system WITH KEY = "environnement"

list.name: projet
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES from system WITH KEY IN (projet) WHERE environnement = '$Environnement'

list.name: role
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES from system WITH KEY IN (role) WHERE projet = '$projet' AND environnement = '$Environnement';

list.label: Server
list.name: server
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM system WITH KEY IN (host) WHERE projet = '$projet' AND role = '$role' AND environnement = '$Environnement'
